properties.Name: StoreServiceLocation
properties.Description: A Service Location that can be found within a Store.

Columns.Name: StoreId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Store.

Columns.Name: ServiceLocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a service location.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period start timestamp of the store / service location relationship.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndTimestamp
Columns.Description: The period end timestamp of the store / service location relationship.

Columns.Name: StoreServiceLocationName
Columns.Description: The name of the Store Service Location.

Columns.Name: StoreServiceLocationDescription
Columns.Description: The description of the Store Service Location.

Columns.Name: StoreServiceLocationTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Store Service Location Type.

Columns.Name: NwLocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: SeLocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: GrossFloorArea
Columns.Description: The total floor area of the Store Service Location including display and support areas such as stock keeping, dressing rooms and building functions.

Columns.Name: NonsellingArea
Columns.Description: The total non-selling square footage of the associated Store Service Location.

Columns.Name: AvailableSellingArea
Columns.Description: The total selling area within the Store Service Location expressed in square footage.
